  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p>“I have need of every man who knows which end of the spear to stab into the <a href=\"/index.php/Wildlings\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Wildlings\">wildlings</a>.” —<a href=\"/index.php/Donal_Noye\" title=\"Donal Noye\">Donal Noye</a><br />“The pointy end.” Jon had told <a href=\"/index.php/Arya_Stark\" title=\"Arya Stark\">his little sister</a> something like that once, he remembered. —<a href=\"/index.php/Jon_Snow\" title=\"Jon Snow\">Jon Snow</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-Rasos55.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rasos55.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></p><div class=\"references-small\">\n<div class=\"mw-references-wrap\"><ol class=\"references\">\n<li id=\"cite_note-Rasos55.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-1\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><a href=\"#cite_ref-Rasos55.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_1-0\">↑</a></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><i><a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords\" title=\"A Storm of Swords\">A Storm of Swords</a></i>, <a href=\"/index.php/A_Storm_of_Swords-Chapter_55\" title=\"A Storm of Swords-Chapter 55\">Chapter 55</a>, Jon VII.</span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n\n<!-- \nNewPP limit report\nCached time: 20260403133015\nCache expiry: 1209600\nDynamic content: false\nCPU time usage: 0.008 seconds\nReal time usage: 0.008 seconds\nPreprocessor visited node count: 121/1000000\nPreprocessor generated node count: 8538/1000000\nPost‐expand include size: 414/2097152 bytes\nTemplate argument size: 22/2097152 bytes\nHighest expansion depth: 8/40\nExpensive parser function count: 0/100\nUnstrip recursion depth: 0/20\nUnstrip post‐expand size: 523/5000000 bytes\n-->\n<!--\nTransclusion expansion time report (%,ms,calls,template)\n100.00%    5.371      1 -total\n 76.07%    4.086      1 Template:Ref\n 51.31%    2.756      1 Template:Ref/core\n 22.79%    1.224      1 Template:References\n-->\n</div>\n<!-- Saved i